sql:
SELECT AVG(fit_rating) AS average_fit_rating
FROM size_feedback
WHERE size_id = 1;

SELECT last_updated
FROM sizes
ORDER BY last_updated DESC;

external_knowledge:
EU region refers to the region with the name 'EU' in the regions table; 
A size is considered to have enough reviews if it has more than 5 feedback entries in the size_feedback table; 
The fit rating is a measure of how well a size fits, with higher ratings indicating a better fit.

sql:
SELECT MAX(feedback_date) AS latest_feedback_date
FROM size_feedback
WHERE size_id = 1;

SELECT rating
FROM size_feedback
WHERE size_id = 1;

SELECT size_id, AVG(rating) AS average_rating
FROM size_feedback
GROUP BY size_id;
